com.datamelt.rules.implementation

Class CheckIsSmallerOrEqual

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.datamelt.rules.implementation.GenericCheck
      • com.datamelt.rules.implementation.CheckIsSmallerOrEqual
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class CheckIsSmallerOrEqual
extends GenericCheck
    Checks if one value is smaller or equal compared to the other value. In case a string value is used, it checks, if the length of the string if smaller or equal to the given length.

    The first parameter of a given method is always the value of the field that shall be checked. The second parameter is either another field to check against or an expected value (fixed value) to check against the first value.

    Author:
    uwe geercken
